01:46:46.608 --> 01:46:48.193
Mommy!

01:46:48.276 --> 01:46:49.111
Nes.

01:46:49.194 --> 01:46:51.530
Mommy!

01:46:52.114 --> 01:46:53.407
Mommy!

01:46:55.534 --> 01:46:56.368
Mommy!

01:46:59.413 --> 01:47:00.956
Mommy!

